<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV76">
<l>puṉpulava ḻiyaṭaitta rakkilacci ṉaiceytu</l>
<l>naṉpulava ḻitiṟantu ñāṉanaṟcu ṭarkoḷīi</l>
<l>yeṉpileḷki neñcuruki yuḷkaṉinte ḻuntatō</l>
<l>raṉpilaṉṟi yāḻiyāṉai yāvarkāṇa vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except thanks to love that rises, with the heart ripening</l>
<l>—by [one’s] blocking the path of the lowly sense organs, sealing [it] with wax,</l>
<l>opening the path of good discernment, lighting the lamp of knowledge,</l>
<l>slighting the house of bones, with the heart melting—</l>
<l rend="indent">who can see the [Lord] with the discus?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
